Recommended fabrications are mounting (cold), digital printing, screen printing, painting, saw cutting, routing, die cut/punch.
Highlights:
- Aluminum composite panels are unbreakable and weather resistant
- Flat surface is great for printing high quality graphics or text.
- Ideal fabrications include mounting, digital prints & more
